    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When you call the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.gameplaykit/documentation/GameplayKit/GKStrategist/bestMoveForActivePlayer()",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method, the Monte Carlo strategist performs an iterative process of randomly choosing moves, searching for a sequence of moves that ends in a win for the current player. At each step in this process, the strategist chooses whether to try a different move or to continue examining the current sequence of moves.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Higher values favor ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "exploration—that is,",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " the strategist becomes more likely to try different moves on each turn. Lower values favor ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "exploitation—that is,",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " the strategist becomes more likely to follow a sequence of moves to a possible endgame. The default value of 4 tends to balance exploration and exploitation. For best results, experiment with different values to find one that provides a style and difficulty of gameplay you prefer for your game.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
